  "text": "A shorter version of this work appeared in [CITATION_1] , in which we discussed the decisions made in designing the user interfaces. Further, the effect on learning of presenting evidence passages in a contrastive format was discussed in [CITATION_2] . This work combines the previous publications and extends it in the following directions.",
